5. Play-to-earn
DPK platform offers multiple gameplays featuring with play-to-earn and GameFi. For example:

Reproduction of Kitties;
Mining mode and KIT tokens;
Staking of DPK and DeFI mode;
Rankings of contribution points for clans and individuals.

More gameplays will be available in the future.
